    description: 'RFK Jr. entered the 2024 race asking questions that no major-party candidate would ask — about regulatory capture, corporate control of government agencies, and the revolving door between industry and the agencies that regulate them. These are legitimate critiques. But his alliance with Trump and his inconsistent positions on fundamental issues undermined his credibility as an independent reformer.',
